    <h2 class="marketing-feature-brief__heading"><a href="#booking" class="js-scroll-link">Track bookings and resources.</a></h2>
    <p class="marketing-feature-brief__description">With a booking system designed specifically for shared spaces, you’ll always know who’s coming, who’s going, and what they’re using.</p>
